snippet.title: Amber Heard Finally Disables Her Instagram Comments Due To Mobs Of Angry Depp Fans! One Last Look..
snippet.description:
I BEGIN READING AMBER'S INSTAGRAM COMMENTS around the 08:12 Mark.
----------------------‐--------------
First things first: 

*I'm an Entertainer, not a Newscaster* 

I left a little surprise at the end for those who watched the entire video..otherwise skip to the best part -🕺🕺💙

 It's a 33 min video. You can binge and enjoy the video in its entirety, or for those who are new to this channel and expect a boring cookie cutter news report that gets right to the point with Zero personality, subscribe to CNN or just skip ahead to the ***8 MINUTE MARK****

THIS ISN'T THE NEWS.....

.......THIS IS THE DARTH NEWS EXPERIENCE 

special performance at the end of the video from Darth around the 29:20 mark. 

#AmberHeard #Mgtow #JusticeForJohnny #Instagram #cringe #DarthNews
